            },
            "plume_of_death": {
              "desc": "<p>晶瑩剔透的人造之羽，古老人類邦國的遺物之一，飛鷹的嘯鳴似乎也被封存其中。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/13/7998136/6fdd4f75d233d1690e845a2db65ba433_1328267447739211369.png",
